      'Embeddable financial marketplaces powering 1,300+ partners with AI-driven monetization, powering 400M inquiries every year and generating $160M+ in annual enterprise revenue.',
    tags: ['FINTECH', 'AI/ML', 'MARKETPLACE'],
  },
  {
    index: '02',
    role: 'Head of Product',
    title: 'Prodigy.fi',
    link: 'https://prodigy.fi/',
    description:
      'On-chain derivatives marketplace turning volatility into yield via fully collateralized dual investment vaults. Live on Base and Berachain with $5M raised.',
    tags: ['DEFI', 'WEB3', 'DERIVATIVES'],
  },
  {
    index: '03',
    role: 'Product Manager',
    title: 'Ocado Smart Platform',
